title: Bridges - Marine Parkway Bridge - [Rockaways - Flatbush Avenue, Brooklyn.]

text:
Marine Parkway Bridge: A set of three views, showing the bridge connecting the Rockaways with Brooklyn via Flatbush Ave. Also seen are the former ferry slips, now obsolete, which formerly carried the traffic that now uses the bridge.

July 24, 1937
Views 1,2 and 3

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
